data.description: Welcome home to your haven of comfort and style! Experience warmth as you cozy up near the fireplace under the new interior paint with a soothing neutral color scheme. The tastefully updated kitchen features an accent backsplash and ample cabinet storage.  Sink into luxury in the primary bathroom complete with double sinks and a separate tub and shower, for a spa-like atmosphere. The primary bedroom is a haven of relaxation, offering a generous walk-in closet. Outside, enjoy your private sanctuary with a patio, perfect for morning coffees. and fenced-in yard offers peace and quietude. The home's partial flooring replacement adds a refreshed look. Exude pleasure in your space; this could be your perfect home sweet home!
